title: LOL Website
body: I can't see the banner thing with all the community links and all of that stuff on top of the page. I have to look in my history to go to boards. How do I fix this? {{champion:32}}

replies.body: That's strange!  Do you have any extensions running that could be causing this?  Try another browser, incognito, or clear your [cache and cookies](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) to see if that will get the top border to return.  Let me know!

It was an extension all along! Thanks for the help, and have a nice day.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
